ch.jacopoc.memento

Class History

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.jacopoc.memento.History

  • public class History
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the states produced by a specific Originator instance. It is possible to orderly traverse it in both directions and branching is supported too.
